code: protected JndiRegistry createRegistry() throws Exception {     myConnectionFactory = new ConnectionFactory().     myConnectionFactory.setHost("myhost").     JndiRegistry registry = super.createRegistry().     registry.bind("myConnectionFactory", myConnectionFactory).     return registry. }

@Test public void testLookupConnectionFactory() throws Exception {     RabbitMQEndpoint endpoint = context.getEndpoint("rabbitmq:myexchange", RabbitMQEndpoint.class).     assertNotNull(endpoint).     assertSame(endpoint.getConnectionFactory(), myConnectionFactory). }
